     How to use:
         icoder [command] <type> data
    
     Commands:
         encode         will encode what to pass
         decode         will uncode what to pass

     Types:
         --url           takes a url(link)
         --char          takes a letter or symbol
         --arquivo or -a    receive file with link list (accepts -l or -s parameters)

         -l              print the links
         -s              saves output to another file

     Example:
         icoder encode --url https://google.com
         icoder encode --char /

         icoder decode --url https%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com
         icoder decode --char %2F
         icoder encode -a file.txt -l